    addNode(101, "bio.txt", "txt", "4.0 K", "2026-03-21", "Hi, I’m Mihai Arisanu, a final-year high school student with a strong interest in computer science. I’m a creative and collaborative person who enjoys working in team environments and contributing to shared goals.\n\nI’m particularly passionate about low-level programming, while also developing practical mobile applications designed to improve everyday life.\n\nOutside of tech, I enjoy playing basketball and following the game whenever I can.", 1);
